high_descs: Go across the room to the table.
Pick up the wine bottle on the table.
Go across the room to the fridge.
Chill the wine in the fridge.
Turn right and go to the table on the left past the fridge.
Set the chilled wine down on the front right corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Set a chilled bottle of wine on the table.

high_descs: Go straight and turn right at the white table.
Pick up the bottle from the table.
Turn right and take two steps and then turn left walk toward the fridge then turn right and face towards the fridge.
Open the Fridge and put the bottle in the fridge and close the fridge and wait to get it cold.
Open the Fridge and take out the bottle then turn right towards the white table on your left then turn right and turn around towards the white table.
Put the bottle on the right corner of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Pick the bottle, cool it and serve on the white table.

high_descs: Walk straight to the wall and then turn left to face the white table.
Pick up the wine bottle from the table.
Turn right, walk towards the door, turn left towards the dishwasher and then turn right to find the fridge.
Place the bottle in the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn right and walk to the middle of the long white table.
Place the wine bottle at the right corner beside the yellow knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled wine bottle next to the yellow knife on the white table.
